articles.title: Jacob Elordi Investigated for Alleged Radio-Producer Assault - Vulture
articles.description: Jacob Elordi is under investigation by the New South Wales Police after allegedly assaulting a radio producer in Australia. The incident occurred after the producer filmed himself on the street asking Elordi sexual questions referencing ‘Saltburn.’
